channel.title: Why does the webclient keep closing?
channel.description: I need some help here. I was trying to go onto the webclient, but the game wouldn't load... So i went to java.com to get the latest update, since i havent updated in a while. Well after i updated it, it would goto the loading screen, get about half way, and then close the browser...wtf? Can somebody please help me?
